348
00:15:19.200 --> 00:15:21.400
It was like. this is a
really useful marketing tool.

349
00:15:21.480 --> 00:15:24.440
- Nobody believed that a
GoldenEye game would work.

350
00:15:24.520 --> 00:15:30.280
Licensed tie-in games at
