00:16:49.760 --> 00:16:51.640
So he was the one powering
through this and saying.

391
00:16:51.720 --> 00:16:53.040
you know. I think
we'd like to do this.

392
00:16:53.120 --> 00:16:54.240
I think we'd like to do that.

